  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/edef626aa2dd4d6ad8205a01ce058a1a.poster.avif?t=1655911391\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/edef626aa2dd4d6ad8205a01ce058a1a.webm?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/edef626aa2dd4d6ad8205a01ce058a1a.mp4?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nummels are dumb but predictable little guys. They’ll always interact with what’s in front of them, even if it’s a chewed up piece of gum. So toss them a ladder, dig a path, place a bridge, or blast a wall. Get them home safely in this medium skill platformer. Use your brain, they won’t use theirs!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Medium skill platforming</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/4447aa3ba8c2bf143e765be5a73eaf31.poster.avif?t=1655911391\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/4447aa3ba8c2bf143e765be5a73eaf31.webm?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/4447aa3ba8c2bf143e765be5a73eaf31.mp4?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nummels can do anything you can do as long as they have the right motivation, but you can run faster and jump higher. This is not a punishingly difficult platformer, but there are challenges for those that want them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go fast to get on the leaderboard</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/0e7e920e9093ee2397d1210060966782.poster.avif?t=1655911391\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/0e7e920e9093ee2397d1210060966782.webm?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/0e7e920e9093ee2397d1210060966782.mp4?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's fine to take your time and set everything up before letting them loose, but to get good scores and unlock all the things, you'll need to go fast.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessorize</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/a18b8e515a4d7b64be3fbc6e77f8784e.poster.avif?t=1655911391\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/a18b8e515a4d7b64be3fbc6e77f8784e.webm?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/a18b8e515a4d7b64be3fbc6e77f8784e.mp4?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get coins by saving Nummels and spend them on cool hats!<br><br><br>A few Nummels may have been harmed during the production of this game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/64e4ee12cd8f10d2582f8cefb8ea3e18.poster.avif?t=1655911391\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/64e4ee12cd8f10d2582f8cefb8ea3e18.webm?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/826470/extras/64e4ee12cd8f10d2582f8cefb8ea3e18.mp4?t=1655911391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
